originalText.text: I just left this parking garage 1/30/24 6pm and did not park here because the attendant was extremely rude. He was busy, and I was waiting patiently when he angrily made a “shoo” motion for me to move my car. He yelled and said he’s busy. I proceeded to let him know that is not the way to deal with a customer. I left and went to another lot in the area.

originalText.text: I had a disappointing experience with this parking facility. The attendant initially quoted a daily rate of $25, we parked at 08h30 am and left at 09h00 ,but when I went to pay, they suddenly charged me $59, claiming that the parking couldn't exceed 12 hours ,they said to me that the attendant had worked there for 10 years,  Misleading and unfair pricing practices, I don’t recommand it
